iedrich_Ebert_(junior)" class="mw-redirect" title="Friedrich Ebert (junior)"><i>Friedrich Ebert</i></a> (1973)<br /><a href="/wiki/Willi_Stoph" title="Willi Stoph">Willi Stoph</a> (1973â1976)<br /><a href="/wiki/Erich_Honecker" title="Erich Honecker">Erich Honecker</a> (1976â1989)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="text-align:left"><span class="nowrap">Prime Minister</span></th><td><a href="/wiki/Otto_Grotewohl" title="Otto Grotewohl">Otto Grotewohl</a> (1957â1964)<br /><a href="/wiki/Willi_Stoph" title="Willi Stoph">Willi Stoph</a> (1964â1973)<br /><a href="/wiki/Horst_Sindermann" title="Horst Sindermann">Horst Sindermann</a> (1973â1976)<br /><a href="/wiki/Willi_Stoph" title="Willi Stoph">Willi Stoph</a> (1976â1989)<br /><a href="/wiki/Hans_Modrow" title="Hans Modrow">Hans Modrow</a> (1989)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="text-align:left">Lieutenant</th><td><a href="/wiki/Walter_Ulbricht" title="Walter Ulbricht">Walter Ulbricht</a> (1957â1971)<br /><a href="/wiki/Erich_Honecker" title="Erich Honecker">Erich Honecker</a> (1971â1989)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="text-align:left"><span class="nowrap">Preceded by</span></th><td><a href="/wiki/Ernst_Wollweber" title="Ernst Wollweber">Ernst Wollweber</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="text-align:left"><span class="nowrap">Succeeded by</span></th><td><a href="/wiki/Wolfgang_Schwanitz" title="Wolfgang Schwanitz">Wolfgang Schwanitz</a></td></tr><tr style="display:none"><td colspan="2">
